     3Ôćĺ## Installing Superstruct
     5ÔćĺTo install Superstruct run:
     6Ôćĺ
     7Ôćĺ```bash
     8Ôćĺnpm install --save superstruct
     9Ôćĺ```
    10Ôćĺ
    11ÔćĺAnd then you can import it:
    12Ôćĺ
    13Ôćĺ```ts
    14Ôćĺimport { object, string, number } from 'superstruct'
    15Ôćĺ
    16Ôćĺconst User = object({
    17Ôćĺ  id: number(),
    18Ôćĺ  name: string(),
    19Ôćĺ})
    20Ôćĺ```
    21Ôćĺ
    22ÔćĺIf you'd like, you can use a wildcard import:
    23Ôćĺ
    24Ôćĺ```ts
    25Ôćĺimport * as s from 'superstruct'
    26Ôćĺ
    27Ôćĺconst User = s.object({
    28Ôćĺ  id: s.number(),
    29Ôćĺ  name: s.string(),
    30Ôćĺ})
    31Ôćĺ```
